Implement curriculum-based staged training.

Do NOT randomly switch all tasks from the beginning.

Training progression:

1. stabilize
2. cruise
3. altitude hold
4. heading hold
5. waypoint follow
6. loiter
7. approach
8. landing
9. mixed missions

Each phase has:
- separate success conditions
- separate rewards
- separate difficulty
- separate environment randomization

Only progress when success threshold achieved.

Example:
if success_rate > 80%:
    unlock next phase

Mixed mission training should only occur after stable mastery of core flight.